description:
For use cases needing longitudinal information of different DICOM studies of the same patient.

Patient level cohesion is maintained with consistent Patient Name and Patient ID across objects of the minimized patient information.
Dates are shifted, while maintaining the distances between the dates, across DICOM studies belonging to the same patient.
Some patient characteristics (age, gender) are kept.
Many technical DICOM header data and some common private tags are kept.
